&lt;p&gt;Result from Using Facade : @@_result&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;button type="button"
    class="[ bg-cyan-500 ] [ text-white ] [ px-4 py-2 ] [ inline-block ] [ rounded-md ] [ inline-flex ] [ space-x-1 ]"
